{
  "stem": "11205.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--March, 1996.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fira, the river Bug--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they made that a border.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it-- I didn't-- you know, it didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it bothered us that the Russians had to leave, and we awaited the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it took two weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans arrived to-- I wrote it down-- the Germans arrived on the 9th of October in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right away somehow, they-- it did-- nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But people start to be terrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the place where I lived, the owner had-- they were-- they had a mill, a flour mill--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also they had in, in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they knew, most probably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they packed up a few, things, and they left on the-- on that-- together when the Russians were still there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And so when the Germans arrived, that was stationed five officers above us in this place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this five officer-- I-- I was so terrified [LAUGHS] of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the Germans came in, they started to catch young people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they, they took them to, to clean the Kasernes and-- in a funny way, we sold clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They asked to take-- people were telling us these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's why I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was sitting home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so they that-- that's what-- they took people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They shaved their beards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we, we heard the stories, and we were really very terrified.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was still-- that was the army, which wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On on the 20th-- I think that was the day I left, the 20th of September-- the 20th of November.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was six weeks still in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, my brother-in-law left before this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He left together with the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meilech.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
